{"tid":1103327,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【乘客注意】港島荃灣觀塘3綫下周起 非繁忙時段每周加開86班車","createTime":"2019-04-12T10:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T11:04:45.000Z","uid":17646,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7cb4c03a456c4beda262a9e241a90ec601f605c8","tid":1103327,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:27:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190412/large/1555055592_f877.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190412%2Flarge%2F1555055592_f877.png&h=b183039a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190412/large/1555060665_36ff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190412%2Flarge%2F1555060665_36ff.png&h=495fba67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190412/large/1555055592_acac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190412%2Flarge%2F1555055592_acac.png&h=0968ae66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港鐵列車長期逼爆，公司宣佈下周一（22日）起，會推出新一輪列車服務改善措施。其中港島綫、荃灣綫和觀塘綫，分別於周五、周末及公眾假期的非繁忙時段，增加額外列車班次，每周合共增加86班車。<br />\n<br />\n根據港鐵提供的資料，港島綫將增加最多班次，每周將加開38班，每逢周五的中午至下午4時49分，會額外增加8班車；至於周日及公眾假期，下午和晚上會分別增加20和10班車。荃灣綫則於周日及公眾假期加車，於上午時段增加14班車。觀塘綫則分別於周六，額外加2班車；周日及公眾假期的部份日間時段，共增加32班車。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵又指，公司自2012年起，於非輕鐵網絡每周累計增加超過3,200班車，輕鐵網絡每周亦已累計增加超過600班車，連同港鐵巴士合計，總載客量超過20億人次。"},{"pid":"25bd636e731ba398d2b6ac1a8fc910595ad0a91d","tid":1103327,"uid":43721,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:31:02.000Z","msg":"想洗準時率<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2702361e7ad05457272c3e3724ce326f89059646","tid":1103327,"uid":126283,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:33:04.000Z","msg":"非繁加開黎把撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cla